title: Judicial Districts, Kansas, 1992
name: Judicial Districts, Kansas, 1992
description:
Abstract: This database comprises 28 State agency boundaries and point of contact. The Kansas Geological Survey collected legal descriptions of the boundaries for various State agencies. The legal descriptions were translated into latitude and longitude coordinates using KGS's LEO and Dpoly software. All coverages are stored as double-precision, with coordinates in units of feet from a projected coordinate space. Note: This data was collected in 1992, boundaries and POCs may have changed. 
Purpose: Produce a series of datasets representing various State agency administrative boundaries. 
Uploaded into Geocommons as shp, dbf, and shx files.
